Roles &amp; Responsibilities
OVERVIEW
The Senior Project Engineer is responsible for delivering quality engineering projects by organizing and controlling all &nbsp;technical, administrative and cost features

Responsibilities

  You are to assist the Project Manager in overseeing the project, planning &amp; ensure work is carry according to schedule.
  Liaise with Consultant on technical issue &amp; doing coordination on site issues with sub-con
  Work with the project team &amp; ability to resolve technical issues

What you’ll need to succeed

  Degree in Mechanical Engrg or&nbsp;equivalent

